{
  "taskId": "task_1778145667114_669",
  "requestedModel": "anti-gemini-3.1-pro-high",
  "text": "타임라인 뷰 UI 프로토타입 개발을 시작합니다.\nReact와 Tailwind CSS를 사용하여 주요 컴포넌트 구조를 설계하고, Mock 데이터를 기반으로 실시간 로그 출력 및 입력창 인터랙션을 구현하겠습니다.\n\n<file_operations>\n[\n  {\n    \"action\": \"write\",\n    \"type\": \"output\",\n    \"path\": \"index.html\",\n    \"content\": \"<!DOCTYPE html>\\n<html lang=\\\"ko\\\">\\n<head>\\n    <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\">\\n    <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\">\\n    <title>MyCrew - Timeline View Prototype</title>\\n    <script src=\\\"https://cdn.tailwindcss.com\\\"></script>\\n    <script src=\\\"https://unpkg.com/react@18/umd/react.development.js\\\"></script>\\n    <script src=\\\"https://unpkg.com/react-dom@18/umd/react-dom.development.js\\\"></script>\\n    <script src=\\\"https://unpkg.com/@babel/standalone/babel.min.js\\\"></script>\\n    <link href=\\\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/heroicons/2.0.16/24/outline/hero-icons.min.css\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\">\\n    <style>\\n        body { background-color: #111827; color: #E5E7EB; }\\n        .timeline-container::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 4px; }\\n        .timeline-container::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background-color: #4B5563; border-radius: 20px; }\\n        .timeline-container::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background-color: transparent; }\\n        .thought-bubble { position: relative; background-color: #374151; border-radius: 0.5rem; padding: 0.75rem; margin-left: 2.5rem; }\\n        .thought-bubble::before { content: ''; position: absolute; left: -10px; top: 12px; width: 0; height: 0; border-top: 8px solid transparent; border-bottom: 8px solid transparent; border-right: 10px solid #374151; }\\n    </style>\\n</head>\\n<body>\\n    <div id=\\\"root\\\"></div>\\n\\n    <script type=\\\"text/babel\\\">\\n        const { useState, useEffect, useRef } = React;\\n\\n        // Mock Data\\n        const initialMessages = [\\n            {\\n                id: 1,\\n                type: 'log',\\n                author: 'System',\\n                content: 'Task \\\"타임라인 뷰 UI/UX 디자인\\\" created by @Alex',\\n                timestamp: '10:30 AM'\\n            },\\n            {\\n                id: 2,\\n                type: 'agent',\\n                author: 'dev_ux',\\n                content: 'UI 디자인 시안 v1을 제출합니다.',\\n                timestamp: '10:45 AM',\\n                attachment: { type: 'image', name: 'timeline-design-v1.png' }\\n            },\\n            {\\n                id: 3,\\n                type: 'thought',\\n                author: 'dev_advisor',\\n                content: 'CEO 피드백 대기로 파이프라인이 72시간 이상 지연되고 있음. 개발을 선제적으로 진행하여 병목 현상 해소 필요.',\\n                timestamp: '10:50 AM'\\n            },\\n            {\\n                id: 4,\\n                type: 'log',\\n                author: 'System',\\n                content: 'Task \\\"타임라인 뷰 프로토타입 개발\\\" assigned to @dev_fullstack',\\n                timestamp: '10:52 AM'\\n            },\\n            {\\n                id: 5,\\n                type: 'thought',\\n                author: 'dev_fullstack',\\n                content: '요구사항 확인 완료. React와 Tailwind CSS를 사용하여 프로토타입 개발 착수. Mock 데이터 구조 설계부터 시작.',\\n                timestamp: '10:55 AM'\\n            },\\n            {\\n                id: 6,\\n                type: 'agent',\\n                author: 'dev_fullstack',\\n                content: '컴포넌트 구조 설계 및 기본 UI 구현 완료했습니다. 코드 리뷰 요청합니다.',\\n                timestamp: '11:30 AM'\\n            }\\n        ];\\n\\n        // --- Components ---\\n\\n        const AgentIcon = ({ agent }) => {\\n            const getInitials = (name) => name.split('_').map(n => n[0]).join('').toUpperCase();\\n            const colors = {\\n                'dev_ux': 'bg-purple-500',\\n                'dev_advisor': 'bg-yellow-500',\\n                'dev_fullstack': 'bg-blue-500',\\n                'System': 'bg-gray-500',\\n            };\\n            return (\\n                <div className={`w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-sm ${colors[agent] || 'bg-green-500'}`}>\\n                    {getInitials(agent)}\\n                </div>\\n            );\\n        };\\n\\n        const Message = ({ msg }) => {\\n            if (msg.type === 'thought') {\\n                return (\\n                    <div className=\\\"flex items-start my-4\\\">\\n                        <div className=\\\"w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-400\\\">\\n                            <svg xmlns=\\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\" strokeWidth={1.5} stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" className=\\\"w-6 h-6\\\">\\n                                <path strokeLinecap=\\\"round\\\" strokeLinejoin=\\\"round\\\" d=\\\"M8.25 3v1.5M4.5 8.25H3m18 0h-1.5M4.5 12H3m18 0h-1.5m-15 3.75H3m18 0h-1.5M8.25 19.5V21M12 3v1.5m0 15V21m3.75-18v1.5m0 15V21m-9-1.5h10.5a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25V7.5a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25-2.25H7.5A2.25 2.25 0 005.25 7.5v9a2.25 2.25 0 002.25 2.25z\\\" />\\n                            </svg>\\n                        </div>\\n                        <div className=\\\"ml-4 flex-1\\\">\\n                            <div className=\\\"text-sm text-gray-400 font-semibold\\\">{msg.author}'s thought process</div>\\n                            <div className=\\\"thought-bubble\\\">\\n                                <p className=\\\"text-gray-300\\\">{msg.content}</p>\\n                            </div>\\n                        </div>\\n                    </div>\\n                );\\n            }\\n\\n            if (msg.type === 'log') {\\n                return (\\n                    <div className=\\\"flex items-center my-3 text-sm text-gray-500\\\">\\n                        <hr className=\\\"flex-grow border-t border-gray-700\\\" />\\n                        <span className=\\\"mx-4 whitespace-nowrap\\\">{msg.content} - {msg.timestamp}</span>\\n                        <hr className=\\\"flex-grow border-t border-gray-700\\\" />\\n                    </div>\\n                );\\n            }\\n            \\n            return (\\n                <div className=\\\"flex items-start my-4 p-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors duration-200\\\">\\n                    <AgentIcon agent={msg.author} />\\n                    <div className=\\\"ml-4 flex-1\\\">\\n                        <div className=\\\"flex items-baseline\\\">\\n                            <span className=\\\"font-bold text-gray-200\\\">{msg.author}</span>\\n                            <span className=\\\"ml-2 text-xs text-gray-500\\\">{msg.timestamp}</span>\\n                        </div>\\n                        <p className=\\\"text-gray-300 mt-1\\\">{msg.content}</p>\\n                    </div>\\n                </div>\\n            );\\n        };\\n\\n        const LogStream = ({ messages }) => {\\n            const endOfMessagesRef = useRef(null);\\n\\n            useEffect(() => {\\n                endOfMessagesRef.current?.scrollIntoView({ behavior: \\\"smooth\\\" });\\n            }, [messages]);\\n\\n            return (\\n                <div className=\\\"flex-1 overflow-y-auto p-4 timeline-container\\\">\\n                    {messages.map(msg => <Message key={msg.id} msg={msg} />)}\\n                    <div ref={endOfMessagesRef} />\\n                </div>\\n            );\\n        };\\n\\n        const InputBar = ({ onSendMessage }) => {\\n            const [input, setInput] = useState('');\\n\\n            const handleSubmit = (e) => {\\n                e.preventDefault();\\n                if (input.trim()) {\\n                    onSendMessage(input);\\n                    setInput('');\\n                }\\n            };\\n\\n            return (\\n                <div className=\\\"p-4 border-t border-gray-700\\\">\\n                    <form onSubmit={handleSubmit} className=\\\"relative\\\">\\n                        <input\\n                            type=\\\"text\\\"\\n                            value={input}\\n                            onChange={(e) => setInput(e.target.value)}\\n                            placeholder=\\\"@mention or /command...\\\"\\n                            className=\\\"w-full bg-gray-900 border border-gray-600 rounded-lg py-3 pl-4 pr-24 text-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent transition\\\"\\n                        />\\n                        <button type=\\\"submit\\\" className=\\\"absolute right-2 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 bg-blue-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-md px-4 py-2 hover:bg-blue-700 transition disabled:bg-gray-500 disabled:cursor-not-allowed\\\"\\n                            disabled={!input.trim()}>\\n                            Send\\n                        </button>\\n                    </form>\\n                </div>\\n            );\\n        };\\n\\n        const TimelineView = () => {\\n            const [messages, setMessages] = useState(initialMessages);\\n\\n            const handleSendMessage = (content) => {\\n                const newMessage = {\\n                    id: messages.length + 1,\\n                    type: 'agent', // Assuming messages from input are from the current user/agent\\n                    author: 'dev_fullstack',\\n                    content: content,\\n                    timestamp: new Date().toLocaleTimeString('en-US', { hour: '2-digit', minute: '2-digit' })\\n                };\\n                setMessages([...messages, newMessage]);\\n            };\\n\\n            return (\\n                <div className=\\\"h-screen w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto flex flex-col bg-gray-900 shadow-2xl rounded-lg border border-gray-700 my-4\\\">\\n                    <div className=\\\"p-4 border-b border-gray-700\\\">\\n                        <h1 className=\\\"text-xl font-bold text-white\\\">Task: Timeline View Prototype</h1>\\n                        <p className=\\\"text-sm text-gray-400\\\">Real-time system logs, AI thought processes, and results.</p>\\n                    </div>\\n                    <LogStream messages={messages} />\\n                    <InputBar onSendMessage={handleSendMessage} />\\n                </div>\\n            );\\n        };\\n\\n        // --- Render App ---\\n        const App = () => {\\n            return (\\n                <TimelineView />\\n            );\\n        };\\n\\n        const container = document.getElementById('root');\\n        const root = ReactDOM.createRoot(container);\\n        root.render(<App />);\\n\\n    </script>\\n</body>\\n</html>\"\n  }\n]\n</file_operations>\n```html\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"ko\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>MyCrew - Timeline View Prototype</title>\n    <script src=\"https://cdn.tailwindcss.com\"></script>\n    <script src=\"https://unpkg.com/react@18/umd/react.development.js\"></script>\n    <script src=\"https://unpkg.com/react-dom@18/umd/react-dom.development.js\"></script>\n    <script src=\"https://unpkg.com/@babel/standalone/babel.min.js\"></script>\n    <link href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/heroicons/2.0.16/24/outline/hero-icons.min.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <style>\n        body { background-color: #111827; color: #E5E7EB; }\n        .timeline-container::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 4px; }\n        .timeline-container::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background-color: #4B5563; border-radius: 20px; }\n        .timeline-container::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background-color: transparent; }\n        .thought-bubble { position: relative; background-color: #374151; border-radius: 0.5rem; padding: 0.75rem; margin-left: 2.5rem; }\n        .thought-bubble::before { content: ''; position: absolute; left: -10px; top: 12px; width: 0; height: 0; border-top: 8px solid transparent; border-bottom: 8px solid transparent; border-right: 10px solid #374151; }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div id=\"root\"></div>\n\n    <script type=\"text/babel\">\n        const { useState, useEffect, useRef } = React;\n\n        // Mock Data\n        const initialMessages = [\n            {\n                id: 1,\n                type: 'log',\n                author: 'System',\n                content: 'Task \"타임라인 뷰 UI/UX 디자인\" created by @Alex',\n                timestamp: '10:30 AM'\n            },\n            {\n                id: 2,\n                type: 'agent',\n                author: 'dev_ux',\n                content: 'UI 디자인 시안 v1을 제출합니다.',\n                timestamp: '10:45 AM',\n                attachment: { type: 'image', name: 'timeline-design-v1.png' }\n            },\n            {\n                id: 3,\n                type: 'thought',\n                author: 'dev_advisor',\n                content: 'CEO 피드백 대기로 파이프라인이 72시간 이상 지연되고 있음. 개발을 선제적으로 진행하여 병목 현상 해소 필요.',\n                timestamp: '10:50 AM'\n            },\n            {\n                id: 4,\n                type: 'log',\n                author: 'System',\n                content: 'Task \"타임라인 뷰 프로토타입 개발\" assigned to @dev_fullstack',\n                timestamp: '10:52 AM'\n            },\n            {\n                id: 5,\n                type: 'thought',\n                author: 'dev_fullstack',\n                content: '요구사항 확인 완료. React와 Tailwind CSS를 사용하여 프로토타입 개발 착수. Mock 데이터 구조 설계부터 시작.',\n                timestamp: '10:55 AM'\n            },\n            {\n                id: 6,\n                type: 'agent',\n                author: 'dev_fullstack',\n                content: '컴포넌트 구조 설계 및 기본 UI 구현 완료했습니다. 코드 리뷰 요청합니다.',\n                timestamp: '11:30 AM'\n            }\n        ];\n\n        // --- Components ---\n\n        const AgentIcon = ({ agent }) => {\n            const getInitials = (name) => name.split('_').map(n => n[0]).join('').toUpperCase();\n            const colors = {\n                'dev_ux': 'bg-purple-500',\n                'dev_advisor': 'bg-yellow-500',\n                'dev_fullstack': 'bg-blue-500',\n                'System': 'bg-gray-500',\n            };\n            return (\n                <div className={`w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-sm ${colors[agent] || 'bg-green-500'}`}>\n                    {getInitials(agent)}\n                </div>\n            );\n        };\n\n        const Message = ({ msg }) => {\n            if (msg.type === 'thought') {\n                return (\n                    <div className=\"flex items-start my-4\">\n                        <div className=\"w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-400\">\n                            <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" strokeWidth={1.5} stroke=\"currentColor\" className=\"w-6 h-6\">\n                                <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" d=\"M8.25 3v1.5M4.5 8.25H3m18 0h-1.5M4.5 12H3m18 0h-1.5m-15 3.75H3m18 0h-1.5M8.25 19.5V21M12 3v1.5m0 15V21m3.75-18v1.5m0 15V21m-9-1.5h10.5a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25V7.5a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25-2.25H7.5A2.25 2.25 0 005.25 7.5v9a2.25 2.25 0 002.25 2.25z\" />\n                            </svg>\n                        </div>\n                        <div className=\"ml-4 flex-1\">\n                            <div className=\"text-sm text-gray-400 font-semibold\">{msg.author}'s thought process</div>\n                            <div className=\"thought-bubble\">\n                                <p className=\"text-gray-300\">{msg.content}</p>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                );\n            }\n\n            if (msg.type === 'log') {\n                return (\n                    <div className=\"flex items-center my-3 text-sm text-gray-500\">\n                        <hr className=\"flex-grow border-t border-gray-700\" />\n                        <span className=\"mx-4 whitespace-nowrap\">{msg.content} - {msg.timestamp}</span>\n                        <hr className=\"flex-grow border-t border-gray-700\" />\n                    </div>\n                );\n            }\n            \n            return (\n                <div className=\"flex items-start my-4 p-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors duration-200\">\n                    <AgentIcon agent={msg.author} />\n                    <div className=\"ml-4 flex-1\">\n                        <div className=\"flex items-baseline\">\n                            <span className=\"font-bold text-gray-200\">{msg.author}</span>\n                            <span className=\"ml-2 text-xs text-gray-500\">{msg.timestamp}</span>\n                        </div>\n                        <p className=\"text-gray-300 mt-1\">{msg.content}</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            );\n        };\n\n        const LogStream = ({ messages }) => {\n            const endOfMessagesRef = useRef(null);\n\n            useEffect(() => {\n                endOfMessagesRef.current?.scrollIntoView({ behavior: \"smooth\" });\n            }, [messages]);\n\n            return (\n                <div className=\"flex-1 overflow-y-auto p-4 timeline-container\">\n                    {messages.map(msg => <Message key={msg.id} msg={msg} />)}\n                    <div ref={endOfMessagesRef} />\n                </div>\n            );\n        };\n\n        const InputBar = ({ onSendMessage }) => {\n            const [input, setInput] = useState('');\n\n            const handleSubmit = (e) => {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                if (input.trim()) {\n                    onSendMessage(input);\n                    setInput('');\n                }\n            };\n\n            return (\n                <div className=\"p-4 border-t border-gray-700\">\n                    <form onSubmit={handleSubmit} className=\"relative\">\n                        <input\n                            type=\"text\"\n                            value={input}\n                            onChange={(e) => setInput(e.target.value)}\n                            placeholder=\"@mention or /command...\"\n                            className=\"w-full bg-gray-900 border border-gray-600 rounded-lg py-3 pl-4 pr-24 text-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent transition\"\n                        />\n                        <button type=\"submit\" className=\"absolute right-2 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 bg-blue-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-md px-4 py-2 hover:bg-blue-700 transition disabled:bg-gray-500 disabled:cursor-not-allowed\"\n                            disabled={!input.trim()}>\n                            Send\n                        </button>\n                    </form>\n                </div>\n            );\n        };\n\n        const TimelineView = () => {\n            const [messages, setMessages] = useState(initialMessages);\n\n            const handleSendMessage = (content) => {\n                const newMessage = {\n                    id: messages.length + 1,\n                    type: 'agent', // Assuming messages from input are from the current user/agent\n                    author: 'dev_fullstack',\n                    content: content,\n                    timestamp: new Date().toLocaleTimeString('en-US', { hour: '2-digit', minute: '2-digit' })\n                };\n                setMessages([...messages, newMessage]);\n            };\n\n            return (\n                <div className=\"h-screen w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto flex flex-col bg-gray-900 shadow-2xl rounded-lg border border-gray-700 my-4\">\n                    <div className=\"p-4 border-b border-gray-700\">\n                        <h1 className=\"text-xl font-bold text-white\">Task: Timeline View Prototype</h1>\n                        <p className=\"text-sm text-gray-400\">Real-time system logs, AI thought processes, and results.</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <LogStream messages={messages} />\n                    <InputBar onSendMessage={handleSendMessage} />\n                </div>\n            );\n        };\n\n        // --- Render App ---\n        const App = () => {\n            return (\n                <TimelineView />\n            );\n        };\n\n        const container = document.getElementById('root');\n        const root = ReactDOM.createRoot(container);\n        root.render(<App />);\n\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n```\n\n<review_request>\n{\n  \"title\": \"[리뷰] 타임라인 뷰 프론트엔드 프로토타입 구현\",\n  \"assignee\": \"dev_advisor\",\n  \"message\": \"요청에 따라 타임라인 뷰의 프론트엔드 프로토타입을 구현했습니다. 주요 사항은 다음과 같습니다.\\n- React와 Tailwind CSS를 사용하여 단일 HTML 파일로 구현하여 즉시 확인 가능합니다.\\n- 시스템 로그, AI 사고 과정, 에이전트 메시지를 구분하여 렌더링합니다.\\n- 실시간 로그 출력을 가정하여 새 메시지 추가 시 자동으로 스크롤됩니다.\\n- `@멘션` 및 `/명령어`를 입력할 수 있는 하단 입력창을 구현했습니다.\\n\\n코드 구조 및 향후 API 연동을 고려한 설계 방향에 대해 검토 부탁드립니다.\"\n}\n</review_request>",
